    <sys:String x:Key="Ui.Verification.Title">Verification Approach</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Ui.Verification.Body">1. Run local preflight and resolve all blocking errors.&#10;2. Package and review generated .intune.json and .intune-checklist.md outputs.&#10;3. Validate install/uninstall/detection in a clean test VM before Intune import.&#10;4. Create app in Intune using the checklist and run pilot assignment first.&#10;5. Confirm detection and uninstall behavior from Intune device logs before broad rollout.</sys:String>

